{"tid":1072415,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓30酒店爆偷拍風暴 逾千住客中招","createTime":"2019-03-22T04:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T05:00:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb28166e2492e561caf6f1e9b3459fb03559eae5","tid":1072415,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190322/20638700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F20638700&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=2003965e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F20638700&h=752a9ef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190322/20638700</a><br />\n<br />\n韓30酒店爆偷拍風暴 逾千住客中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190322/large/a2106a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190322%2Flarge%2Fa2106a.gif&h=5e405c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓揭發酒店房間內遭人暗設攝錄機並將偷拍片段放上網，有約1,600名酒店住客疑被偷拍，四名疑犯中有兩人已落網。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主謀扮顧客裝針孔鏡<br />\n<br />\n警方指涉案者自去年8月起在全國10個城市30間酒店的42個房間，將僅得1毫米的偷拍鏡頭（圖，紅圈示）放置在電視機頂盒、風筒和電源插座，並將803條偷拍片段上載至去年開設的海外網站甚至直播，於過去三個月賺取700萬韓圜（4.87萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n一名主謀被指以顧客身份進入酒店安裝鏡頭，另一人被控負責開設和管理網站，另外兩人被指協助購買偷拍鏡頭和付款維持網站運作。該網站有逾4,000會員，97人每月付44.95美元（350港元）。警方指今次是首次有人因直播偷拍影像被捕。<br />\n<br />\n南韓偷拍問題嚴重，警方於去年錄得逾6,600宗偷拍案，約20%性侵受害者被偷拍，比2008年的3.6%為高。去年有數萬名女性多次上街抗議偷拍風氣和性暴力，高呼「我的人生不是你的色情片」，要求政府加強罰則。當局去年11月修例，任何非法拍攝或未經當事人同意發佈有關影像，可被監禁五年或罰款3,000萬韓圜（20.86萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社/美國有線新聞網絡  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n歐盟︰英須通過協議才可押後脫歐"},{"pid":"2c0f9ab0f187e69b3158b0771a16863bdacaaea3","tid":1072415,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"好似差咁啲嘢"},{"pid":"7133207a273ee8e11f38536f54df25e519d2d01c","tid":1072415,"uid":132847,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"0647132341dfe5b162b7a7b5608bbce89867b35f","tid":1072415,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"萬寧酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be0b14e4d86cbd4428b00f608ae4cd266204489","tid":1072415,"uid":200834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"死人放火嗰啲po就高清圖 呢啲就連張144p都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ae2c3eea557ca63e32fac33a6714c12a2a37d8","tid":1072415,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"香港都唔好得去邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633913695079bd725501a8b9478f688d422fedb6","tid":1072415,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:46:40.000Z","msg":"大生意，搞咁多野，每月賺幾皮"},{"pid":"998d40ad727c404bb0395964c34528cbd6e206f6","tid":1072415,"uid":172925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">南韓揭發酒店房間內遭人暗設攝錄機並將偷拍片段放上網</span><br />\n片呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e546997406649d5ffd38d2ca0c8ff7aff8c8fa","tid":1072415,"uid":6024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:54:26.000Z","msg":"好多酒店都會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e5331fb7d560e9fa7c050873f82c2ec1d8f37c","tid":1072415,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be0b14e4d86cbd4428b00f608ae4cd266204489","tid":1072415,"uid":200834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"死人放火嗰啲po就高清圖